title: Ranked anyone?^.^
body: I've been playing League for awhile now, and i think im ready to give ranked a shot but kinda bit nervous to actually start haha, anyone wanna que together or anything? Strictly for fun, i in no way want to que with anyone who believes telling other people how bad they are or anything toxic like that. :D

replies.body: Yes please, just added you. Love the summoner name btw. Meed to get out of this Bronze hell.
